  <summary date="2020-03-16T15:28:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Provide Accurate Information Directly Act or PAID Act

This bill requires the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services to identify, in response to an inquiry from certain non-group health plans (e.g., liability insurers), whether an individual was enrolled in Medicare, Medicare Advantage, or the Medicare prescription drug benefit during the preceding three-year period.</summary>
